      <div class="prose">
        <p>Both Workiz and Jobber integrate well with specialized HVAC tools. Consider these additions to maximize your software investment:</p>
        
        <p><strong>Time Tracking:</strong> <a href="https://get.toggl.com/f71dwhbrzvzz" rel="sponsored nofollow">Toggl Track</a> helps monitor technician productivity and job profitability. HVAC contractors using time tracking see 12-15% improvements in job costing accuracy.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Lead Generation:</strong> <a href="https://get.apollo.io/fxnpnadnv4lb" rel="sponsored nofollow">Apollo.io</a> provides contact data for commercial HVAC prospects. The platform helps identify facility managers and building owners in your service area, supporting business development efforts.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Call Tracking:</strong> Understanding which marketing efforts drive calls matters for HVAC growth. Our <a href="/hvac/call-tracking/best-call-tracking-for-hvac">call tracking guide</a> covers tools that integrate with both platforms.</p>
      </div>

